en_US.DialogText: I'm not a hard hearted man

zh_CN.DialogText: 反正已经有不少人欠我一份人情了。

en_US.DialogText: Anyway, many people already owe me a favor.

zh_CN.DialogText: 而且你应该也是公社成员了吧？我们互相照顾是应该的

en_US.DialogText: What's more, nationality is still National. Isn't it meaningless now?

zh_CN.DialogText: 我都不知道这里究竟被什么东西炸了，你的家乡也一样吧？

en_US.DialogText: I don't even know what was blown up here. It's probably a nuclear bomb, biological and chemical weapons. Is your hometown the same?

zh_CN.DialogText: 我们都回不去以前的家了....

en_US.DialogText: We can't go back to our old home....

zh_CN.DialogText: 是啊，更何况，发射核弹的那些人和你我也没什么关系吧？
这里是一些我藏身处的一些包裹，不知道里面有什么大概也没有装着食物，给你当礼物吧

en_US.DialogText: Here are some packages in my hiding place. I don't know what's in them.Probably no food. Let me give you a gift of thanks

zh_CN.DialogText: 或许这样的收获还不错？
在末日前的所有的虚幻的想象的共同体，现在已经没有意义了...

en_US.DialogText: All the illusory imaginary communities before the end of the day are meaningless now

zh_CN.DialogText: 先想办法一起活下去吧

en_US.DialogText: Let's find a way to live together
